        <p style="margin-top: 2%;text-align: justify;">At Kavya's Makeup Academy, where we turn makeup enthusiasts into professional makeup artists. If you're passionate about makeup and dream of turning your talent into a rewarding career, you've come to the right place. Our makeup artist training classes are designed to provide you with the knowledge, skills, and confidence you need to flourish in the exciting world of makeup artistry.</p>
        <h4>Our Makeup Artist Training Classes:</h4>
        <ul style="text-align: justify;">
            <li><b>Fundamentals of Makeup:</b> Our foundation course covers the basics of makeup artistry, introducing you to essential techniques, tools, and products. You'll learn how to create a flawless base, work with color theory, and adapt makeup for different occasions and skin types.</li>
            <li><b>Advanced Makeup Techniques:</b> Dive deeper into the art of makeup with advanced classes that cover topics such as contouring, highlighting, specialized eye makeup, and dramatic looks. Our experienced instructors will help you master the skills needed to create stunning makeup transformations.</li>
            <li><b>Bridal and Special Occasion Makeup:</b> Specialize in bridal and special occasion makeup, where you'll learn how to enhance a bride's natural beauty and create timeless, elegant looks for weddings and other significant events.</li>
            <li><b>Fashion and Editorial Makeup:</b> Unleash your creativity and explore the high-fashion world of makeup artistry. Our fashion and editorial makeup classes teach you the skills required for photoshoots, runway shows, and editorial spreads.</li>
        <li><b>Business and Marketing:</b> Learn how to kickstart your career as a makeup artist with courses on business management and marketing. We'll help you understand how to build your portfolio, network with clients, and establish your brand.</li>
        </ul>
